    "en": {
      "title": "Normal Level Examination Answer Sheet Evaluation Work Begins Again",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Examinations has announced that it has decided to resume the second phase of the answer sheet evaluation work of the G.E.D.",
        "Because of that, G.P.D. The evaluation work of the second phase of the Ordinary Level Examination has been temporarily suspended.",
        "The evaluation of the said answer sheet will be resumed from the 6th of August. However, preliminary answer paper evaluation work has been completed successfully, he said.",
        "G.E.T. which was temporarily stopped. He mentioned that he requested to follow the proper procedure to get fuel to the teachers who are engaged in the answer sheet work before starting the second phase of the regular examination."
      ],
